ished.\n","docLink":"./Init/Data/Iterators/Basic.html#Std.IterStep.successor","kind":"def","line":243,"name":"Std.IterStep.successor","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Init/Data/Iterators/Basic.lean#L243-L251"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/Iterators/Basic.html#Std.IterStep.done\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">IterStep</span>.<span class=\"name\">done</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Sort</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">β</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Sort</a> u_2}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Data/Iterators/Basic.html#Std.IterStep\">IterStep</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span> <span class=\"fn\">β</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"`IterStep.done` describes the situation that an iterator has finished and will neither emit\nmore values nor cause any monadic effects. In this case, no succeeding iterator is provided.\n","docLink":"./Init/Data/Iterators/Basic.html#Std.IterStep.done","kind":"ctor","line":237,"name":"Std.IterStep.done","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/95583d74bd14ff8cc2b789347d15dfdad1259f97/src/Init/Data/Iterators/Basic.lean#L237-L241"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Init/Data/Iterators/Basic.html#Std.IterStep.skip\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">IterStep</span>.<span class=\"name\">skip</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span clas